shard-listener
Copyright 2026 Lightweb Inc. (https://lightweb.net)

=========================================================================

This software subscribes to IPv6 multicast shard groups produced by the
BSV transaction sharding pipeline, applies configurable shard and subtree
filters, and forwards matching transaction frames to a downstream unicast
consumer over UDP or TCP. Gap detection and NACK-based recovery are
performed per sender per shard group.

