Third-Party Standards

The v1 wire-frame format (FrameVerV1 = 0x01) processed by this software
transports transactions conforming to BRC-12: Raw Transaction Format,
a published standard maintained by BSV Blockchain:

  BRC-12: Raw Transaction Format
  BSV Blockchain Standards Repository
  https://github.com/bitcoin-sv/BRCs/blob/master/transactions/0012.md

